{"tid":689566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓或未能承擔住宿費用 有傳星美願代為支付","createTime":"2018-06-04T07:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T08:28:26.000Z","uid":37757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5de1dff4946731faac1278cb59d05f8a0ce8703d","tid":689566,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"美朝峰會如期本月12日於新加坡舉行，北韓領導人金正恩住宿成焦點。消息指，金正恩或心儀入住獅城最豪華的富麗敦酒店（The Fullerton Hotel）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/finance/images/stories/16/2018/06/843401180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.etnet.com.hk%2Ffinance%2Fimages%2Fstories%2F16%2F2018%2F06%2F843401180.jpg&h=7c1635a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美朝峰會如期本月12日於新加坡舉行，北韓領導人金正恩或心儀入住獅城最豪華的富麗敦酒店（圖)。 (iStock圖片)<br />\n<br />\n這間五星級酒店的總統套房一晚房價約6,000美元（約4.68萬港元），北韓希望其他國家支付，美方據報亦願意承擔北韓官員住宿費，正設法體面解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/finance/images/stories/16/2018/06/HKET_20180604_A20_01_aL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.etnet.com.hk%2Ffinance%2Fimages%2Fstories%2F16%2F2018%2F06%2FHKET_20180604_A20_01_aL.jpg&h=c77e57ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>星先代付 免平壤視為侮辱</strong><br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》引述匿名美方官員報道，美方對於替北韓支付費用一事持開放態度，但擔心平壤會視之為美方侮辱北韓。因此，華府為顧全北韓面子，正考慮要求新加坡政府先墊支北韓代表團的住宿費用，美方稍後再暗中向獅城付款。<br />\n　<br />\n　　新加坡國防部長黃永宏出席亞洲安全會議時稱，新加坡願意支付美朝峰會部分開支，包括保安措施等小量費用，但沒有提及北韓人員住宿問題。<br />\n　<br />\n　　美國國務院發言人諾爾特（Heather Nauert）則指，美方並未要求第三方支付北韓的費用。<br />\n　<br />\n　　北韓國務委員會部長金昌善等人目前於新加坡籌備美朝峰會，據報下榻富麗敦酒店。外界估計北韓屬意於美朝峰會期間，安排金正恩一行人入住這間酒店。<br />\n　<br />\n　　<span style=\"color: red;\">由於北韓長期受到國際孤立及制裁，導致缺乏資金，情況在該國代表出國時尤見明顯。近至今年南韓平昌冬奧，北韓派出啦啦隊、藝術團、官員代表團等南下，南韓政府為他們繳付了260萬美元開支；國際奧委會則負責了22名北韓運動員的帳單。<br />\n　</span><br />\n　　至於美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）則料在美朝峰會期間入住香格里拉酒店，主因該處保安嚴密。白宮及國務院均拒絕回應。該酒店剛舉行了亞洲安全會議，有多國防長和高官出席。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c32bd04700a48501f64f6ad6526d76adc8cb56","tid":689566,"uid":59570,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"住酒店都冇錢，<br />\n仲話對抗美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399937a6dcc542e5e4cd9c79ffe0b0bfe19fb795","tid":689566,"uid":37757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"72c32bd04700a48501f64f6ad6526d76adc8cb56","tid":689566,"uid":59570,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"住酒店都冇錢，<br />\n仲話對抗美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"連登仔集資比金仔，到時可以手持acoount係北韓屌韓妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b4c03b834ee99f86c6898315a7d46b691f6b82","tid":689566,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"399937a6dcc542e5e4cd9c79ffe0b0bfe19fb795","tid":689566,"uid":37757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"72c32bd04700a48501f64f6ad6526d76adc8cb56","tid":689566,"uid":59570,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"住酒店都冇錢，<br />\n仲話對抗美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"連登仔集資比金仔，到時可以手持acoount係北韓屌韓妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc89963abd6654ba6ba4dd262ea40f4bf64134b2","tid":689566,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"講唔嚟都唔怕人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\